## 4. NestJS Module Breakdown

### Module Dependency Graph

```mermaid
graph LR
    Auth --> Users
    Users --> Vendors
    Catalog --> Vendors
    Catalog --> Search
    Inventory --> Catalog
    Orders --> Inventory
    Orders --> Users
    Orders --> Payments
    Fulfillment --> Orders
    Notifications --> Orders
    Notifications --> Fulfillment
    Audit["AuditModule"] -.-> Auth
    Audit -.-> Orders
    Audit -.-> Vendors
```

### Module Details

| Module                  | Responsibility                                                           | Key Endpoints                                                                      |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **AuthModule**          | JWT issue/verify, login/register, password reset, refresh token rotation | `POST /auth/login`, `POST /auth/register`, `POST /auth/refresh`                    |
| **UsersModule**         | User CRUD, role/membership management, profile                           | `GET /users/me`, `PATCH /users/me`, `GET /admin/users`                             |
| **VendorsModule**       | Vendor onboarding, store settings, approval workflow                     | `POST /vendors/apply`, `POST /admin/vendors/:id/approve`, `PATCH /vendor/settings` |
| **CatalogModule**       | Products CRUD, categories, attributes, ES sync                           | `POST /vendor/products`, `GET /catalog/products`, `GET /catalog/products/:slug`    |
| **InventoryModule**     | Stock levels, reservations, low-stock alerts                             | `PATCH /vendor/inventory/:sku`, `GET /vendor/inventory`                            |
| **OrdersModule**        | Cart, checkout (TX), order lifecycle, refunds                            | `POST /orders/checkout`, `GET /account/orders`, `GET /vendor/orders`               |
| **PaymentsModule**      | Stripe Connect integration, payout tracking                              | `POST /payments/intent`, `POST /webhooks/stripe`                                   |
| **FulfillmentModule**   | Shipments, carrier integration, tracking webhooks                        | `POST /fulfillment/ship`, `GET /tracking/:orderId`, `POST /webhooks/shipping`      |
| **SearchModule**        | ES index management, query building                                      | `GET /search/products?q=...&facets=...`                                            |
| **NotificationsModule** | Email (SES/Resend), SMS, in-app, push                                    | Internal event consumer only                                                       |
| **AuditModule**         | Immutable audit trail for security-critical actions                      | Internal interceptor — no public endpoints                                         |
| **HealthModule**        | Terminus health checks                                                   | `GET /health`                                                                      |

### RBAC Model

```typescript
// roles: 'platform_admin' | 'vendor_owner' | 'vendor_staff' | 'customer'
// Guard chain: JwtAuthGuard → RolesGuard → optional AbilityGuard (CASL)

@UseGuards(JwtAuthGuard, RolesGuard)
@Roles('vendor_owner', 'vendor_staff')
@Post('vendor/products')
createProduct(@Body() dto: CreateProductDto, @CurrentUser() user: UserContext) {}
```

